  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a medium bowl, mix together flour, peanut butter, and mustard to form crust mixture.",
    "Press crust mixture into the bottom of a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together tempeh, cheddar cheese, and mozzarella cheese.",
    "Spread tempeh mixture over crust mixture.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until the crust is golden brown and the tempeh is heated through.",
    "Garnish with chopped scallions and serve hot.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste."
